title: Popbot 01-07 Symbolic Machine Code-A - Ashley Wood
description:
This is a high quality scan I have done myself of the hardcover collection of Popbot 01 to 07. The series seems to be in limbo for quite some time now, but it is still worthwhile to check out for the amazing art alone. 

As always: the scans hardly do the the awesome print quality of the oversized original book justice. If you like it, buy it so that Ashley Wood has a reason to return to this project.
